EVERY SINGLE PLACE
THAT WE CAN THINK OF.

40
00:04:04,429 --> 00:04:05,229
- HMM.

41
00:04:05,263 --> 00:04:07,329
I HAVEN'T TOLD THE OTHERS,

42
00:04:07,363 --> 00:04:09,963
BUT INUYASHA IS
REALLY TORMENTED.

43
00:04:09,996 --> 00:04:12,296
