TO SORT THINGS OUT ON HIS OWN.

45
00:04:13,863 --> 00:04:17,063
BUT I CAN'T STAND THE THOUGHT
OF WAITING IT OUT.

46
00:04:17,096 --> 00:04:19,329
I'M SO WORRIED.

47
00:04:25,863 --> 00:04:30,296
- I'M VERY DISAPPOINTED
IN YOU, INUYASHA.

48
00:04:30,329 --> 00:04:33,163
IT'S HARD TO BELIEVE
YOU STILL HAVE TROUBLE

49
00:04:33,196 --> 00:04:34,829
WIELDING THE TETSUSAIGA.

50
00:04:34,863 --> 00:04:35,929
- THAT'S WHY I'M ASKING YOU

51
00:04:35,963 --> 00:04:39,163
TO MAKE MY SWORD LIGHTER,
OLD MAN.

52
00:04:39,196 --> 00:04:40,896
THERE MUST BE SOME WAY.

53
00:04:40,929 --> 00:04:43,596
- THEN WHY DON'T YOU
FIGURE IT OUT?

54
00:04:43,629 --> 00:04:46,363
- I'M IN A HURRY, OK?

55
00:04:46,396 --> 00:04:50,296
AND BESIDES, I DON'T WANT
TO TRANSFORM ANYMORE.

56
00:04:50,329 --> 00:04:51,729
- UH...

57
00:04:51,763 --> 00:04:54,096
