- AHH.

66
00:05:21,396 --> 00:05:24,629
MASTER INUYASHA,
NICE TO TASTE YOU AGAIN.

67
00:05:24,663 --> 00:05:26,829
[GRUNTING]

68
00:05:26,863 --> 00:05:29,163
AND HERE I WAS
WORRIED ABOUT YOU.

69
00:05:29,196 --> 00:05:32,963
- SO THIS IS WHERE
YOU'VE BEEN HIDING OUT, IS IT?

70
00:05:32,996 --> 00:05:34,996
