ABOUT THE SWORD, MYOGA.

72
00:05:36,296 --> 00:05:39,096
- HUH?
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

73
00:05:39,129 --> 00:05:40,129
- DON'T ACT INNOCENT!

74
00:05:40,163 --> 00:05:42,963
YOU'RE THE ONE WHO TOLD HER
ABOUT THE TETSUSAIGA.

75
00:05:42,996 --> 00:05:45,629
KAGOME SAID THAT MY SWORD IS

76
00:05:45,663 --> 00:05:49,229
WHAT KEEPS MY DEMON NATURE
IN CHECK.

77
00:05:50,129 --> 00:05:51,263
- HMM.

78
00:05:51,296 --> 00:05:52,329
WELL, THAT FIGURES.

