KEEP HOLD OF MY SWORD.

84
00:06:00,896 --> 00:06:03,763
[CRYING]

85
00:06:03,796 --> 00:06:04,663
- UHH.

86
00:06:04,696 --> 00:06:07,796
- I HAVE TO MASTER
THE TETSUSAIGA, OR ELSE.

87
00:06:07,829 --> 00:06:10,329
THAT'S THE ONLY WAY.

88
00:06:10,363 --> 00:06:11,463
- HMM.

89
00:06:11,496 --> 00:06:14,496
