ENOUGH TRANSFORMATIONS.

91
00:06:18,496 --> 00:06:20,663
- YEAH.

92
00:06:23,363 --> 00:06:26,929
- WELL, THAT LEAVES
BUT ONE CHOICE.

93
00:06:26,963 --> 00:06:27,896
- HUH?

94
00:06:27,929 --> 00:06:32,329
- INUYASHA, YOU MUST
KILL RYUKOTSUSEI.

95
00:06:32,363 --> 00:06:34,996
- RYUKOTSUSEI?

96
00:06:35,029 --> 00:06:36,829
- WHO?
- HMM?

97
00:06:36,863 --> 00:06:40,829
- YOU DIDN'T SAY
RYUKOTSUSEI, DID YOU?

98
00:06:44,263 --> 00:06:46,863
- HE IS THE DEMON
YOUR FATHER BATTLED

99
00:06:46,896 --> 00:06:50,829
AND SEALED INTO A DORMANT SLEEP.

100
00:06:53,529 --> 00:06:55,663
INUYASHA, WHY DO YOU THINK

101
00:06:55,696 --> 00:06:58,463
