HAS NOT YET REACHED

103
00:07:01,863 --> 00:07:05,196
THE POWER OF YOUR FATHER'S.

104
00:07:07,929 --> 00:07:12,129
- IN OTHER WORDS, IF I DESTROY
THE DEMON MY FATHER FOUGHT,

105
00:07:12,163 --> 00:07:14,863
THEN I'LL SURPASS
THE OLD MAN IN STRENGTH?

106
00:07:14,896 --> 00:07:16,596
- NOW, LISTEN, MASTER INUYASHA.

107
00:07:16,629 --> 00:07:21,329
BY DESTROY, ALL YOU HAVE TO DO
IS PIERCE THE DEMON'S HEART

108
00:07:21,363 --> 00:07:23,496
SINCE HIS POWERS
STILL LIE DORMANT.

109
00:07:23,529 --> 00:07:27,029
- WHAT?
I DON'T HAVE TO FIGHT HIM?
[BUZZING]

110
00:07:27,063 --> 00:07:27,829
- OF COURSE NOT.

111
00:07:27,863 --> 00:07:29,196
IT TOOK EVERY OUNCE OF STRENGTH

112
00:07:29,229 --> 00:07:31,529
FOR YOUR FATHER TO PUT
THIS DEMON UNDER SEAL.

113
00:07:31,563 --> 00:07:34,329
HE WASN'T ABLE TO LEVY
A FINISHING BLOW.

114
00:07:34,363 --> 00:07:36,629
- SO NOW I'M THE ONE
WHO GETS STUCK

115
00:07:36,663 --> 00:07:38,129
SLAYING HIM LIKE A COWARD.

116
00:07:38,163 --> 00:07:41,796
- IF YOU KEEP COMPLAINING,
I WILL NOT SHOW YOU THE WAY.
OH!

117
00:07:41,829 --> 00:07:44,696
- JUST WHO DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE TALKING TO, MYOGA?

118
00:07:44,729 --> 00:07:47,529
- OH, I JUST--
[GRUNTING]

119
00:07:47,563 --> 00:07:49,896
[BUZZING]

120
00:07:53,063 --> 00:07:54,163
- HMM.

121
00:07:54,196 --> 00:07:56,629
VERY INTERESTING, KANNA.

122
00:07:56,663 --> 00:07:58,996
I'VE DISPATCHED YOU, KAGURA,

123
00:07:59,029 --> 00:08:02,529
GOSHINKI, JUROMARU,
AND KAGEROMARU,

124
00:08:02,563 --> 00:08:06,263
AND NOT A SINGLE ONE OF YOU
WERE ABLE TO PUT AN END

125
00:08:06,296 --> 00:08:08,729
TO INUYASHA.
HMM.

126
00:08:08,763 --> 00:08:14,463
LET'S GIVE THIS RYUKOTSUSEI
A TRY, SHALL WE?

127
00:08:14,496 --> 00:08:18,096
[LAUGHS EVILLY]

128
00:08:27,829 --> 00:08:30,129
- UHH. UHH.

129
00:08:39,496 --> 00:08:41,263
[GRUNTING]

130
00:08:41,296 --> 00:08:43,829
- HOW MUCH FURTHER
IS IT, MYOGA?

131
00:08:43,863 --> 00:08:46,463
- NOT MUCH.
WE'LL BE ABLE TO SEE IT SOON.

132
00:08:46,496 --> 00:08:47,196
KEEP MOVING.

133
00:08:47,229 --> 00:08:51,963
- UHH.
I SHOULD SQUASH YOU.
UHH.

134
00:08:54,063 --> 00:08:55,829
- TOTOSAI.

135
00:08:55,863 --> 00:08:57,463
- HMM?

136
00:08:58,896 --> 00:09:01,363
WHAT ARE YOU YOUNGSTERS
DOING HERE?

137
00:09:01,396 --> 00:09:03,263
- WE'RE LOOKING FOR INUYASHA.

138
00:09:03,296 --> 00:09:05,696
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHERE HE IS?

139
00:09:05,729 --> 00:09:08,129
- INUYASHA?

140
00:09:08,163 --> 00:09:08,996
HMM.

141
00:09:09,029 --> 00:09:11,196
