142
00:09:11,229 --> 00:09:13,096
INUYASHA, YOU SAY.

143
00:09:13,129 --> 00:09:15,329
- HE'S HAVING TROUBLE
WIELDING THE TETSUSAIGA,

144
00:09:15,363 --> 00:09:18,396
SO WE THOUGHT HE MIGHT HAVE
COME TO SEE YOU FOR HELP.

145
00:09:18,429 --> 00:09:21,996
- LET ME SEE.
WHAT TO DO?

146
00:09:22,029 --> 00:09:23,396
- YOU KNOW, DON'T YOU?

147
00:09:23,429 --> 00:09:27,063
WHERE IS HE?
TELL ME!
[SCREAMING]

148
00:09:27,096 --> 00:09:29,296
- OOH!
[CRASH]

149
00:09:29,329 --> 00:09:31,396
- SORRY ABOUT THAT.
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

150
00:09:31,429 --> 00:09:36,296
- INUYASHA HAS GONE
TO THE VALLEY OF RYUKOTSUSEI.

151
00:09:36,329 --> 00:09:39,629
- THE VALLEY OF RYUKOTSUSEI?

152
00:09:39,663 --> 00:09:41,129
- HUH?

153
00:09:41,529 --> 00:09:42,963
- UHH.
UHH.

