00:09:42,996 --> 00:09:47,096
- LOOK, MASTER INUYASHA,
OVER THERE.

155
00:10:02,029 --> 00:10:04,396
- OH.

156
00:10:05,029 --> 00:10:06,896
SO THAT'S RYUKOTSUSEI.

157
00:10:06,929 --> 00:10:07,929
- CORRECT.

158
00:10:07,963 --> 00:10:10,696
AND LOOK WHERE YOUR FATHER'S
CLAW HAS PIERCED HIM,

159
00:10:10,729 --> 00:10:16,629
