RIGHT ABOVE HIS HEART.

160
00:10:17,963 --> 00:10:21,363
- HUH?

161
00:10:22,796 --> 00:10:25,729
[LAUGHING]

162
00:10:25,763 --> 00:10:27,729
- NARAKU.

163
00:10:27,763 --> 00:10:32,496
[LAUGHING]

164
00:10:33,463 --> 00:10:34,829
