TO MASTER THE TETSUSAIGA,

166
00:10:38,363 --> 00:10:40,496
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL HIM EARLIER?

167
00:10:40,529 --> 00:10:43,563
[CHEWING]
- THAT WOULD HAVE BEEN TOO EASY.

168
00:10:43,596 --> 00:10:48,296
