ALL THE ANSWERS, NOW, WILL HE?
HUH?

169
00:10:48,329 --> 00:10:52,963
- I THINK THAT INUYASHA
HAS ALREADY SUFFERED ENOUGH.

170
00:10:52,996 --> 00:10:55,029
- POOR THING.

171
00:10:55,063 --> 00:10:57,229
- HE AGONIZED
OVER WHAT HE'D DONE.

172
00:10:57,263 --> 00:10:59,663
THAT'S WHY HE CAME TO SEE YOU.

173
00:10:59,696 --> 00:11:00,563
- THAT'S TRUE.

174
00:11:00,596 --> 00:11:01,896
- EVEN THOUGH THEY WERE BANDITS,

175
00:11:01,929 --> 00:11:05,829
THE FACT REMAINS THAT THEY WERE
STILL HUMAN BEINGS
THAT HE KILLED.

176
00:11:05,863 --> 00:11:06,796
[SCOFFS]

177
00:11:06,829 --> 00:11:09,229
- THAT'S WHY I TOLD HIM
WHAT HE NEEDED TO DO.

178
