IF HE'D FELT NOTHING
AFTER KILLING THOSE HUMANS,

179
00:11:12,763 --> 00:11:17,463
HE'D HAVE NO RIGHT
TO WIELD THE TETSUSAIGA.

180
00:11:18,963 --> 00:11:22,929
- NARAKU, WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

181
00:11:34,129 --> 00:11:38,196
