- THAT CLAW SEALS HIS POWERS.

182
00:11:43,096 --> 00:11:47,129
[SHUDDERING]

183
00:11:51,063 --> 00:11:54,596
[SHUDDERING]

184
00:12:16,096 --> 00:12:17,529
[LAUGHS]

185
00:12:17,563 --> 00:12:22,763
- RYUKOTSUSEI, OVER YONDER
STANDS THE SON OF THE DEMON

186
00:12:22,796 --> 00:12:24,863
WHO HURLED YOU INTO DORMANCY.

187
00:12:24,896 --> 00:12:29,396
DO WITH HIM AS YOU PLEASE.

188
00:12:30,229 --> 00:12:32,696
OH...

189
00:12:44,096 --> 00:12:46,629
[GRUNTING]

190
00:12:52,096 --> 00:12:53,763
[GROWLS]

191
00:12:53,796 --> 00:12:54,596
- THIS IS TERRIBLE!

192
00:12:54,629 --> 00:12:56,463
WE MUST FLEE, MASTER INUYASHA!

193
00:12:56,496 --> 00:12:58,596
- WHAT?
YOU MUST BE OUT OF YOUR MIND.

194
00:12:58,629 --> 00:13:02,096
THIS WAY IS MUCH BETTER THAN
SLAYING A DEFENSELESS DEMON

195
00:13:02,129 --> 00:13:04,229
LIKE I WAS SOME KIND
OF PATHETIC COWARD.

196
00:13:04,263 --> 00:13:07,496
IF I'M GONNA MAKE
THE TETSUSAIGA LIGHTER,

197
00:13:07,529 --> 00:13:10,629
THEN I WANT TO FACE HIM
HEAD TO HEAD.

198
00:13:10,663 --> 00:13:12,163
I'M GONNA TAKE YOU OUT.

199
00:13:12,196 --> 00:13:17,396
- LITTLE MAN, YOU THINK THAT
YOU CAN DESTROY ME?

200
00:13:17,429 --> 00:13:19,229
[LAUGHS]

201
