202
00:13:21,929 --> 00:13:23,863
THIS SHALL PROVE AMUSING.

203
00:13:23,896 --> 00:13:26,029
- AMUSING?

204
00:13:28,429 --> 00:13:29,863
UHH!

205
00:13:32,563 --> 00:13:34,229
UHH.

206
00:13:34,263 --> 00:13:35,629
UHH.

207
00:13:35,663 --> 00:13:38,463
UHH. UHHH!

208
00:13:38,496 --> 00:13:40,496
- NO!
IT'S HOPELESS!

209
00:13:40,529 --> 00:13:42,229
[WHIMPERING]

210
00:13:42,263 --> 00:13:45,296
- AHHH!

211
00:13:45,329 --> 00:13:47,096
UHH.

212
00:13:47,396 --> 00:13:49,263
- SUCH AN EASY MARK.

213
00:14:02,329 --> 00:14:03,896
- UHH.

214
00:14:03,929 --> 00:14:05,363
[CHUCKLES]

215
00:14:05,396 --> 00:14:07,496
[LAUGHING]

216
00:14:07,529 --> 00:14:09,929
- HMM?

217
00:14:18,129 --> 00:14:19,229
- AHH.

218
00:14:19,263 --> 00:14:22,263
THAT DEMON IS REMARKABLE.

219
00:14:22,296 --> 00:14:26,896
IT SHOULD BE EASY FOR HIM
TO OVERCOME INUYASHA.

220
00:14:26,929 --> 00:14:31,229
I SHALL ENJOY THIS PERFORMANCE.

221
00:14:31,263 --> 00:14:34,063
- A MERE DEMON PUPPET.

222
00:14:34,096 --> 00:14:36,963
HARDLY A WARRIOR.

223
00:14:37,763 --> 00:14:41,596
- SO HE WAS GOING AFTER NARAKU
FROM THE START.

224
00:14:41,629 --> 00:14:43,129
- LITTLE MAN,

225
00:14:43,163 --> 00:14:44,763
I HOPE YOU'LL PROVIDE ME

226
00:14:44,796 --> 00:14:47,863
