227
00:14:47,896 --> 00:14:49,763
- HA.

228
00:14:49,796 --> 00:14:51,796
MORE THAN HAPPY TO OBLIGE YOU.

229
00:14:51,829 --> 00:14:55,629
- THIS LOOKS LIKE
A NEW DEVELOPMENT.

230
00:14:55,663 --> 00:14:59,196
- IT'S A DEMON AURA.

231
00:14:59,229 --> 00:15:03,063
- AAH...MAYBE SOMETHING BAD
HAS HAPPENED.

232
00:15:03,096 --> 00:15:07,696
- TOTOSAI, DOES THAT MEAN
HE'S IN TROUBLE?

233
00:15:07,729 --> 00:15:08,829
- OH, THAT FOOL.

234
00:15:08,863 --> 00:15:10,663
HE HAS AWAKENED RYUKOTSUSEI.

235
00:15:10,696 --> 00:15:13,363
- I'VE NEVER FELT
SUCH AN OMINOUS AURA.

236
00:15:13,396 --> 00:15:16,096
- THEN THIS DEMON
INUYASHA'S GONE TO FIGHT

237
00:15:16,129 --> 00:15:17,496
