- KAGOME.

239
00:15:20,729 --> 00:15:23,829
- I THINK WE SHOULD ALL
GO AND HELP HIM.

240
00:15:23,863 --> 00:15:26,663
- HEY, WAIT FOR ME!

241
00:15:28,663 --> 00:15:29,929
- OH, DEAR.

242
00:15:29,963 --> 00:15:32,696
WHAT A MISERABLE DAY.

243
00:15:39,696 --> 00:15:41,063
- COME AT ME, LITTLE MAN.

244
00:15:41,096 --> 00:15:43,129
DON'T DENY ME
SOME ENTERTAINMENT.

245
00:15:43,163 --> 00:15:47,596
- HUH, I'M THE ONE
WHO'S GONNA BE ENTERTAINED.

246
00:15:49,129 --> 00:15:51,929
THE SCAR LEFT
BY MY FATHER'S CLAW.

247
00:15:51,963 --> 00:15:53,563
IF I CAN PIERCE HIM THERE,

248
00:15:53,596 --> 00:15:56,763
THE TETSUSAIGA
WILL BECOME LIGHTER.

249
00:15:58,363 --> 00:16:00,296
[SCREAMING]

250
00:16:00,329 --> 00:16:02,096
YAAA!

251
00:16:02,129 --> 00:16:05,296
HEH.
HUH?

252
00:16:05,329 --> 00:16:09,796
[GRUNTING]

253
00:16:09,829 --> 00:16:13,463
THE TETSUSAIGA COULDN'T
CUT THROUGH HIS THICK SKIN.

254
00:16:13,496 --> 00:16:18,163
- SEE?
IT'S USELESS, NO MATTER
HOW HARD YOU TRY.

255
00:16:18,196 --> 00:16:22,696
MY BODY IS MIGHTIER THAN ARMOR.

256
00:16:28,163 --> 00:16:30,629
[GASPS]

257
00:16:41,924 --> 00:16:44,990
- UHH!
UHH!

258
00:16:45,024 --> 00:16:47,724
UHH.

259
00:16:47,757 --> 00:16:49,724
UHH.
UHH.

260
00:16:49,757 --> 00:16:51,690
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

261
00:16:51,724 --> 00:16:55,024
- M-MASTER INUYASHA,
WE DON'T STAND A CHANCE!

262
00:16:55,057 --> 00:16:55,824
- SAVE IT.

263
00:16:55,857 --> 00:16:58,457
THIS BATTLE IS
JUST GETTING STARTED.

264
00:16:58,490 --> 00:16:59,590
- I ALREADY TOLD YOU

265
00:16:59,624 --> 00:17:02,124
IT TOOK EVERYTHING
IN YOUR FATHER'S POWER

266
00:17:02,157 --> 00:17:03,557
TO RENDER HIM DORMANT.

267
00:17:03,590 --> 00:17:08,257
MORE IMPORTANTLY, THE WOUND
INFLICTED UPON YOUR FATHER
DURING THE BATTLE

268
00:17:08,290 --> 00:17:11,857
WAS ULTIMATELY WHAT KILLED HIM.

269
00:17:11,890 --> 00:17:14,724
- HUH?
UH.

270
00:17:14,757 --> 00:17:18,357
- SO HE PERISHED, DID HE?

271
00:17:18,390 --> 00:17:23,224
AND YOU ARE THAT WRETCH'S SON?

272
00:17:24,224 --> 00:17:27,224
DON'T TELL ME
YOU CAME TO AVENGE HIM

273
00:17:27,257 --> 00:17:29,724
WITH THAT
RIDICULOUS LITTLE SWORD.

274
00:17:29,757 --> 00:17:32,957
- HUH, UNFORTUNATELY,
I DON'T EVEN REMEMBER

275
00:17:32,990 --> 00:17:34,524
WHAT MY OLD MAN LOOKED LIKE.

276
00:17:34,557 --> 00:17:38,324
AS IF I WOULD EVEN CARE ABOUT
AVENGING HIS DEATH.

277
00:17:38,357 --> 00:17:40,157
- WHAT?!
HOW DARE YOU SAY THAT?

278
00:17:40,190 --> 00:17:41,490
YOU'VE BEEN SAVED
COUNTLESS TIMES

279
00:17:41,524 --> 00:17:44,690
BY THE VERY SWORD THAT
YOUR FATHER PASSED DOWN TO YOU.

280
00:17:44,724 --> 00:17:45,890
- STOP INTERFERING.

281
00:17:45,924 --> 00:17:47,024
- TRAITOROUS SON.

282
00:17:47,057 --> 00:17:51,457
I'LL HAVE NOTHING
TO DO WITH YOU.
[SOBBING]

283
00:17:51,490 --> 00:17:55,757
- RIGHT.
I KNOW YOU'RE JUST RUNNING AWAY.
HUH?

284
00:17:55,790 --> 00:17:58,590
UHH!

285
00:17:58,624 --> 00:18:00,157
UHH.

286
00:18:00,890 --> 00:18:02,790
UHH.

287
00:18:02,824 --> 00:18:05,557
UHH.
DAMN!

288
00:18:06,324 --> 00:18:10,457
MY FANGS USED TO REPAIR
MY BROKEN TETSUSAIGA,

289
00:18:10,490 --> 00:18:11,890
AND THE REASON IT'S SO HEAVY

290
00:18:11,924 --> 00:18:15,290
IS BECAUSE I'M NOT
AS STRONG AS MY FATHER WAS.

291
00:18:15,324 --> 00:18:17,257
I KNOW.

292
00:18:17,290 --> 00:18:20,757
I MUST SOMEHOW
DESTROY RYUKOTSUSEI

293
00:18:20,790 --> 00:18:24,290
AND SURPASS MY FATHER IN POWER.

294
00:18:27,557 --> 00:18:29,290
[GRUNTING]

295
00:18:29,324 --> 00:18:32,657
[SCREAMING]

296
00:18:34,224 --> 00:18:37,290
- WHAT AN OMINOUS AURA.

297
00:18:37,324 --> 00:18:38,757
- THIS ISN'T A GOOD SIGN.

298
00:18:38,790 --> 00:18:43,190
- HOW COULD RYUKOTSUSEI
HAVE BEEN BROUGHT
OUT OF DORMANCY?

299
00:18:43,224 --> 00:18:44,224
- AS IF I'D KNOW.

300
00:18:44,257 --> 00:18:48,224
I MUST SAY THAT IT POSES
QUITE THE PROBLEM, THOUGH.

301
00:18:48,257 --> 00:18:49,024
[SIGHS]

302
00:18:49,057 --> 00:18:50,924
- IF RYUKOTSUSEI
RISES UP ONCE MORE,

303
00:18:50,957 --> 00:18:55,024
THE PLAINS OF MUSOSHI WILL BE
RAZED TO A FIELD OF ASHES.

304
00:18:55,057 --> 00:18:58,857
- OH, IS HE REALLY
THAT FRIGHTENING A DEMON?

305
00:18:58,890 --> 00:18:59,824
- YES.

306
00:18:59,857 --> 00:19:02,224
- HOW CAN WE POSSIBLY
HOPE TO STOP HIM, THEN?

307
00:19:02,257 --> 00:19:05,757
- THERE'S ONLY ONE WAY TO STOP
THE REAWAKENED RYUKOTSUSEI.

308
00:19:05,790 --> 00:19:09,490
HE MUST USE THE BAKURUYUHA,
OR BACKLASH WAVE.

309
00:19:09,524 --> 00:19:11,890
- BACKLASH WAVE?
WHAT'S THAT?

310
00:19:11,924 --> 00:19:15,557
- A POWERFUL ULTIMATE TECHNIQUE
OF THE TETSUSAIGA.

311
00:19:15,590 --> 00:19:18,324
- YOU MEAN IT'S EVEN STRONGER
THAN THE WINDSCAR?

312
00:19:18,357 --> 00:19:22,924
- THE WINDSCAR IS
A MERE TRICK FOR NOVICES.

313
00:19:22,957 --> 00:19:23,924
- IT IS?

314
00:19:23,957 --> 00:19:26,557
BUT INUYASHA CAN'T EVEN
HOLD UP THE TETSUSAIGA,

315
00:19:26,590 --> 00:19:28,924
LET ALONE USE THE WINDSCAR.

316
00:19:28,957 --> 00:19:31,790
HE CAN'T MASTER A NEW TECHNIQUE.

317
00:19:31,824 --> 00:19:35,457
- I SUPPOSE YOU'RE RIGHT.

318
00:19:36,724 --> 00:19:39,257
[SQUEAKING]
- HMM?

319
00:19:39,290 --> 00:19:40,390
[GRUNTING]

320
00:19:40,424 --> 00:19:46,190
MYOGA, HAVE YOU RUN OUT
ON INUYASHA YET AGAIN?
KAGOME!

321
00:19:46,224 --> 00:19:47,524
[SHUDDERS]

322
00:19:47,557 --> 00:19:49,490
- INUYASHA.

323
00:19:49,857 --> 00:19:52,257
I HOPE YOU'RE OK.

324
00:19:53,690 --> 00:19:55,757
[GRUNTING]

325
00:20:13,924 --> 00:20:14,957
- PITIFUL.

326
00:20:14,990 --> 00:20:17,857
THIS IS MORE TEDIOUS
THAN I EXPECTED.

327
00:20:17,890 --> 00:20:19,457
DESTROYING YOU DOES NOTHING

328
00:20:19,490 --> 00:20:23,257
TO RELIEVE THE ANGER I FEEL
TOWARDS YOUR FATHER!

329
00:20:23,290 --> 00:20:25,057
- UHH.

330
00:20:25,090 --> 00:20:29,490
UHH.
[SCREAMING]
UHH.

331
00:20:30,124 --> 00:20:32,357
[GRUNTING]

332
00:20:32,390 --> 00:20:36,757
- DO YOU NOT UNDERSTAND
THAT YOU CANNOT SLAY ME

333
00:20:36,790 --> 00:20:39,424
WITH SUCH AN INFERIOR SWORD?

334
00:20:39,457 --> 00:20:42,190
[GRUNTING]

335
00:20:44,190 --> 00:20:48,724
[GRUNTING]

336
00:20:49,690 --> 00:20:52,690
[GRUNTING]
[GASPS]

337
00:20:52,724 --> 00:20:54,357
- TETSUSAIGA!

338
00:20:54,390 --> 00:20:57,990
- INUYASHA, YOU MUSTN'T
PART WITH THE TETSUSAIGA.

339
00:20:58,024 --> 00:20:59,190
WHEN YOUR LIFE IS IN DANGER,

340
00:20:59,224 --> 00:21:03,157
YOUR DEMON NATURE
WILL TAKE CONTROL OF YOU.

341
00:21:09,190 --> 00:21:10,924
- UHH.

342
00:21:11,957 --> 00:21:17,724
[GRUNTING]
TETSUSAIGA.

343
00:21:28,757 --> 00:21:32,157
- I SEE THEM!
OVER THERE!

344
00:21:33,090 --> 00:21:34,757
[GASPS]

345
00:21:44,490 --> 00:21:48,924
- HOW PATHETIC.
CRUSHED ALREADY.

346
00:21:48,957 --> 00:21:50,424
HMM?

347
00:21:51,424 --> 00:21:52,724
[HEARTBEAT]

348
00:21:52,757 --> 00:21:56,090
WHAT IS HAPPENING?

349
00:21:56,124 --> 00:21:59,390
- INUYASHA.
- HMM?

350
00:22:01,290 --> 00:22:02,024
- OH, NO!

351
00:22:02,057 --> 00:22:05,124
INUYASHA ISN'T
HOLDING TETSUSAIGA!

352
00:22:05,157 --> 00:22:11,124
[HEARTBEAT]

353
00:22:11,157 --> 00:22:13,357
- INUYASHA!

354
00:22:13,390 --> 00:22:18,824
[GROWLING]
- KAGOME.

355
00:22:22,491 --> 00:22:26,224
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

356
00:23:58,999 --> 00:24:01,133
- INUYASHA TRANSFORMS
INTO A DEMON.

357
00:24:01,166 --> 00:24:05,366
IF WE STICK AROUND,
HE MIGHT EVEN COME
AFTER US, TOO.

358
00:24:05,399 --> 00:24:09,833
TOTOSAI WANTS US TO LEAVE,
BUT I WON'T ABANDON INUYASHA.

359
00:24:09,866 --> 00:24:11,933
NOT NOW,
WHEN HE'S TRYING SO HARD

360
00:24:11,966 --> 00:24:13,933
TO DISCOVER HIS TRUE POWER.

361
00:24:13,966 --> 00:24:15,333
WAIT.

362
00:24:15,366 --> 00:24:19,099
THE TETSUSAIGA
IS STARTING TO PULSATE.

363
00:24:20,666 --> 00:24:24,733
NEXT TIME...

364
00:24:24,766 --> 00:24:25,766
SEE YOU SOON.

